Elizabeth M. Jeffrey et al. v. Planning and Zoning Board of Appeals of the Town of Greenwich et al. Submitted December 18, 1967 decided February 27, 1968 Submitted January 9

decided February 27, 1968

Orson L. St. John, in support of the motion. George W. Scott, Jr., in opposition. George W. Scott, Jr., in support of the motion. Orson L. St. John, in opposition.

The motion by the defendant the Young Women’s Christian Association of Greenwich, Connecticut, Inc., for a review of the taxation of costs in the Supreme Court having been considered, the court finds nothing erroneous in the clerk’s taxation of costs in the appeal from the Court of Common Pleas in Fairfield County at Stamford.

The motion by the plaintiffs for a review of the taxation of costs in the appeal from the Court of Common Pleas in Fairfield County at Stamford is denied.
